OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late brightness.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fwith variable amounts of cloud. Patchy
OL,9,Ffrost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,12,Fwith some spells of hazy sunshine,
OL,13,Fsome high cloud around. Mild inland
OL,14,Fbut a chilly onshore breeze along
OL,15,Feastern coastal districts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
